{"tid":1419203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"偏聽捉鬼文化，我怕有一人前線衝衝下，拎轉頭只係得返自己","createTime":"2019-08-06T00:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T00:31:36.000Z","uid":271843,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"13c88d79ab81c6cb0f1001e52b4a41f67b7666b7","tid":1419203,"uid":271843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:22:14.000Z","msg":"我知P牌有原罪<br />\n但你啱的意見咪聽<br />\n唔啱的意見咪唔聽<br />\n<br />\n唔駛下下話風向post 唔駛理<br />\np牌係鬼。<br />\n<br />\n勸前線一步已經最唔鬼的行為<br />\n唔勸，由前線畀人捉晒<br />\n最後咪又係我哋啲冷氣軍師來攞彩<br />\n<br />\n勸君<br />\n「當與怪獸搏鬥時，千萬不要令自己也成為怪獸」<br />\n「不要被仇恨蒙敝雙眼」<br />\n「我哋唔係狗，我哋會反省」<br />\n<br />\n大家語氣唔好，唔代表喺鬼<br />\n係鬼就叫你衝最過火，之後連登少你一個"},{"pid":"3e1ca2e56abf3b29550ba7d887d507e76ddb2b42","tid":1419203,"uid":271843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:22:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"32f838ed4070c70693098b5f5786f696437ee7db","tid":1419203,"uid":271843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:22:48.000Z","msg":"又推"},{"pid":"06ac81c416739ee786b80309a5b3055a8a79bd0a","tid":1419203,"uid":271843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:23:00.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"35d16a4fbac94b646068efb651829e689cc3eb39","tid":1419203,"uid":271843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:23:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7cf0c1cf4e29ec7d5fbac30d08c62fb44a63fc5f","tid":1419203,"uid":58351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:23:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8d686b5200794225b82c0b849711518c6aa86498","tid":1419203,"uid":271843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T00:31:36.000Z","msg":"「當與怪獸搏鬥時，千萬不要令自己也成為怪獸」"}]}